  "slug": "smoky",
  "type": "annotation",
  "title": "The smoky candle end of time",
  "sourceFile": "Burbank_notes/smoky_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>the smoky\n        candle end...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>A complex line, which combines Mantegna's image of\n        history as a burning candle, Shelley's image of esthetic\n        perception as a burning coal, and Bleistein's cigar. It\n        marks that stage at which Bleistein achieves the third of\n        Aquinas aesthetic perceptions, which is that of <em>claritas</em>.\n        </p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>Bleistein and Shylock</td>\n<td><a href=\"Stonesi_JR.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "the smoky candle end... A complex line, which combines Mantegna's image of history as a burning candle, Shelley's image of esthetic perception as a burning coal, and Bleistein's cigar. It marks that stage at which Bleistein achieves the third of Aquinas aesthetic perceptions, which is that of claritas . reference topics Bleistein and Shylock Structural analysis back to \"Burbank\"",
